Usage: bar [-h, --help] [COMMAND] [OPTION]
small utiliity written in shellscript for restarting, launching and turning off the polybar status bar.

COMMANDS:
	restart [-a, --all] [bar name]		restart the bar specified by bar name or all active bars
	kill [-a, --all] [bar nmae]		kill the bar specified by bar name or all active bars
	launch [bar name]			launch bar specified by bar name

For more information see "man bar"
